@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Support";
}

<section class="page-shell">
    <span class="eyebrow">Support</span>
    <h1>Ajuda, evidencias e canais publicos</h1>
    <p class="lead">
        Esta area centraliza os pontos publicos de orientacao do app. O objetivo e facilitar
        validacao em campo e reduzir dependencia de links soltos.
    </p>

    <div class="info-grid">
        <article class="panel">
            <h2>Hub publico</h2>
            <p>Repositorio publico de distribuicao, releases e arquivos visiveis para usuarios.</p>
            <a class="primary-link" href="https://github.com/Erikalellis/DDSStudyOS-Updates">Abrir DDSStudyOS-Updates</a>
        </article>

        <article class="panel">
            <h2>Roadmap</h2>
            <p>Estado da base atual, trilha Phoebe e diretriz do DDS Study Pass.</p>
            <a class="primary-link" href="https://github.com/Erikalellis/DDSStudyOS-Updates/blob/main/ROADMAP_PUBLIC.md">Abrir roadmap publico</a>
        </article>

        <article class="panel">
            <h2>Evidencias tecnicas</h2>
            <p>Smoke tests, rollout e comprovacoes tecnicas da linha publicada.</p>
            <a class="primary-link" href="https://github.com/Erikalellis/DDSStudyOS-Updates/releases">Abrir evidencias e releases</a>
        </article>
    </div>

    <a class="back-link" href="/">Voltar para a home publica</a>
</section>

<style>
    .page-shell {
        max-width: 1040px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 36px 24px 48px;
    }
    .eyebrow {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: #7c5cff;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    h1 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        color: #eef2ff;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
        line-height: 1.05;
    }
    .lead, .panel p {
        color: #c9d4ea;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .info-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 18px;
        margin-top: 28px;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    }
    .panel {
        border: 1px solid rgba(164, 180, 215, 0.16);
        border-radius: 24px;
        background: rgba(8, 14, 30, 0.84);
        padding: 22px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    }
    .panel h2 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        color: #f6f8ff;
        font-size: 1.08rem;
    }
    .primary-link, .back-link {
        color: #8ea6ff;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    .back-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        margin-top: 24px;
    }
</style>
